description.displayText: Josslynn provided childcare for my son from 6 months until he was a year old, so she worked with him through lots of milestones, was flexible, fun, and patient. I feel very lucky that she was there for my little one through his first year:)

description.displayText: Josslyn provided truly exceptional care for my son, O. O. was always excited to see her on arrival and happy when I'd come home at the end of her shift. She worked with him from when he was about 3 months, until recently, and is now a year old. She was attentive to his changing needs as he grew this past year. My only regret is not being able to provide her full time work to keep her in Brooklyn. But our loss is Philadelphia's gain!
